    "• FewRel (Han et al, 2018).",
    "The FewRel dataset comes in two iterations, denoted as versions 1.0 and 2.0.",
    "The inaugural version, 1.0, represents the pioneering integration of few-shot learning with RE.",
    "The training set incorporates 64 distinct relationships, and the test set comprises 16 relationships.",
    "Version 2.0 introduces challenges in domain adaptation and the detection of categories not covered above, evaluating the models' transferability and OOD generalization capabilities."
